{"tid":1016655,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不用依靠外來移民] 匈牙利政府鼓勵生育　婦女有四名以上孩子免交稅","createTime":"2019-02-11T01:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T01:16:10.000Z","uid":37232,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"956f244d61e5513c8770066abbee76c4328b817f","tid":1016655,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T01:15:55.000Z","msg":"匈牙利政府宣布，為了鼓勵生育，增加國家人口，擁有四個或以上子女的婦女，可終生豁免繳交入息稅。<br />\n<br />\n立場反移民的總理歐爾班在年度國會演說中表示，不用依靠外來移民填補國家人口，強調這是捍衛國家未來的舉措。<br />\n<br />\n匈牙利每年人口減少32000人，當地婦女生育率低於歐盟平均水平。<br />\n<br />\n其他鼓勵生育的措施包括為至少有兩名子女的家庭，提供補貼住房貸款計劃，以及購買汽車補貼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1442221-20190211.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1442221-20190211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo5wcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=f20061c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1442221-20190211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ce4556df\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1442221-20190211.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"47b6a8f0078d0a6574fee1520e191973df82b5ed","tid":1016655,"uid":209248,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T01:20:15.000Z","msg":"人地國家咁好"},{"pid":"6a6ab3698d6b70d02fa7c3b2c6f25dfdfd27fbab","tid":1016655,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T01:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a811c512f1b830a0b811c56745227295f1718b","tid":1016655,"uid":58685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T01:49:16.000Z","msg":"刷首抽都好"},{"pid":"ef678a6e01980c4b43f8582ef9bed798d73970d8","tid":1016655,"uid":43428,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T02:06:20.000Z","msg":"我地香港呢邊好多人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />